{"tid":1284014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就好像一盤髒水 你不可能在這盤水中 只想保存自己乾淨的部分","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:40:34.000Z","uid":8131,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4539aa7fcf32c6df6ae4379f98a1e4e6866a6890","tid":1284014,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RzOwobCxnHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRzOwobCxnHk&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=ec1f5754\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RzOwobCxnHk</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你身在何處 在中國所鋪排的政治旋渦裡 沒有人是可以獨善其身的 就好像一盤髒水 你不可能在這盤水中 只想保存自己乾淨的部分<br />\n<br />\n自由就像我們呼吸的空氣一樣 一般人會覺得這是多麼理所當然的事情 但是只有當空氣逐漸稀薄的時候 我們才會感受到空氣的重要 自由的可貴<br />\n<br />\n香港人一直告訴我們 請踏在香港的屍體上想台灣的路 可是我們更想和香港人說 讓我們一起共同尋找 一個沒有中國威權獨裁打壓的幸福可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7617ad48d9f89d19017a32673fcf6b52a6de5f","tid":1284014,"uid":8131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/08xPR755MPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F08xPR755MPI&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=b5c78fb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/08xPR755MPI</a><br />\nWe stop being ourselves when we stop standing up for the things that matter"},{"pid":"301fdb11c621f444c68b779bfdd3fedaa5222a29","tid":1284014,"uid":8131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"全世界都支持梗我地架 唔好放棄啊 每一個人都好重要！<br />\n<br />\nCarry on HongKongers!"},{"pid":"6a67a47ec3a5cd380f2b3d9d1463eb99894b0994","tid":1284014,"uid":8131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你 </code></pre>"},{"pid":"03b44c99979349c167e0d411f53df7064d386e3b","tid":1284014,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08: